### typeview â€” Preview typefaces

1. clone repository
2. run `.\typeview.ps1 path\to\font\repository`
3. wait for cache and compile

--

Switches:

`-Update` - rebuild font cache (cache will build on first run in selected directory)
`-AddShortcut` - add a shortcut to the desktop for compiled webview
`-OpenInBrowser` - open after compile is finished

.\typeview.ps1 path\to\font\repository -Update -AddShortcut -OpenInBrowser

--

Open manually:

1. go to `path\to\font\repository`
2. open index.html
3. play with fonts

--

Changelog:

v0.4.0 - add filter
v0.3.0 - add switches
v0.2.0 - optimization and improvememnts
v0.1.0 - initial release

